Package selrach.bnetbuilder.model.distributions.conditional

Class Summary
AbstractConditionalDistribution The abstract implementation of a conditional distribution, all distributions should eventually stem from this
ConditionalTable This is a distribution for a discrete variable with only discrete parents.
GaussianMix Distribution for a continuous variable with only discrete parents
LinearGaussian Distribution for continuous variable with only continuous parents, this is linear in the sense that the mean is a linear combination of each parent value.
LinearGaussianMix Distribution for a continuous variable that has both discrete and continuous parents.
Mixture This handles a generalized mixture of discrete and continuous components
MultinomialSigmoid This is a distribution for a discrete variable that has continuous parents
MultinomialSigmoidMix This is a distribution for a discrete variable that has both discrete and continuous parents.
